        <p>The first step is to understand what attestation your specific document requires. Send us a photo of your document via WhatsApp and tell us what you need it for. We will review it and explain the complete chain required, including realistic timelines and costs.</p>
        
        <p>If your document is already partially attested, we can advise on remaining steps. If attestation has been attempted but rejected, we can identify the issue and suggest how to proceed.</p>
        
        <p>For complete document packages—such as all documents needed for a <a href="/services/golden-visa-translation/">Golden Visa application</a> or family sponsorship—we coordinate the timing so all documents are ready together, avoiding situations where some documents expire while waiting for others.</p>
        
        <p>Attestation timelines depend on factors beyond our control, but we provide honest estimates based on current processing times. We keep you informed throughout the process so you always know where your documents are and when to expect them.</p>
      </div>
